<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.8">
<l>maṇṇiṉmī pāraṅ keṭuppāṉ maṟamaṉṉar</l>
<l>paṇṇiṉmēl vanta paṭaiyellām pāratattu</l>
<l>viṇṇiṉmī tēṟa vicayaṉtē rūrntāṉai</l>
<l>naṇṇināṉ nāṭi naṟaiyūril kaṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having searched for and approached the one</l>
<l>Who drove Vijaya’s chariot so that all the bold kings’ armies,</l>
<l>Which came on [horse] saddles in the Bhārata [War],</l>
<l>Rose up to the heavens, to remove that burden upon the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">I saw [him] in Naṟaiyūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
